        <li>Presented on developing <strong>APIs with Flask</strong> for NLP tasks such as lemmatization and named entity recognition using spaCy.</li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
      title="Computer Skills Education Volunteer"
      subtitle="Fundación Laudes Infantis"
      date="Jul 2022 – Jun 2023"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Taught <strong>basic robotics</strong> to children in low-income areas of Bogotá, empowering dozens of individuals with hands-on STEM skills.</li>
